Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.83,KARA-english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:16.38,KARA-japanese,,0000,0000,0000,,{\kf25}It{\kf8}su{\kf83}ka {\kf18}bo{\kf25}ku {\kf41}ga {\kf36}mis{\kf47}ete {\kf50}a{\kf74}ger{\kf101}u {\kf20}hi{\kf23}kar{\kf26}i {\kf40}no {\kf11}ka{\kf33}gayak{\kf207}u {\kf31}se{\kf25}ka{\kf41}i {\kf14}w{\kf475}o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:16.38,KARA-english,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I'll show you a world that shines in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}is the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... is the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you ask Rem to kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, {\alpha&HFF&}I want to be loved by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I want to be loved by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... {\alpha&HFF&}just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is going to die... just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.59,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(365,331)}Gamble
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when do you want him killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me to him, I'll kill him instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The earlier, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could even be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it may be a little careless to decide straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I'll think carefully about when and how we should kill him, and I'll give you my answer after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. {\alpha&HFF&}No matter what happens, don't kill until I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. No matter what happens, don't kill until I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can promise you that... {\alpha&HFF&}with regard to L...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can promise you that... with regard to L...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, give me your cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather slow on the uptake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me yours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that when you're part of a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, I'm being marked by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, they have the ability to bug specific telephone lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! In that case, have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa will give you one of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I started to use each for a different purpose, I ended up with three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours should probably be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'll give you a love call every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And send you lots of texts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be leaving the phone switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you only when necessary, and ensure that information is kept to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... {\alpha&HFF&}when will you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... when will you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether we go ahead with killing L or not, I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like the call is going to be very romantic, but if we can talk love afterwards, I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Misa, you'd better go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?! It's only 7 pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time for lovers has only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go grab something to eat together, and follow that by watching the sun set, and then it'll be time to get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For today, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when you talk to Rem outside, make sure no one is around, and do so quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do the same with Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san! Please come again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty surprised when you just kissed her out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's necessary to ensure that Misa falls utterly in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I need to decide whether or not to kill L tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ryuuga's identity as L isn't publicly known, I've got to be prepared for the fact that if he dies, I will be strongly suspected of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that since you declared yourselves to be friends, you might be having second thoughts about killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Friends"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went along with what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning I've said, "if he wants friendship, I'll take it".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Yagami Light, Ryuuga is merely a friend for appearance's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is Kira's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. L is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's revealed himself to me as L, I'll have to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make it an "accidental death", hardly anyone will suspect that I'm Kira, and even if they do, there'll be no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine what will happen after L dies... {\alpha&HFF&}this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine what will happen after L dies... this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, L... or rather Ryuuzaki or Ryuuga, will be your last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crumbs from snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die in the next few days, your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say, Ryuuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Where's this suddenly coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange it so that you can use Watari as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest will be up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! You said that the majority of your suspicions had already been dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How deeply do you really suspect my son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I really understand what I truly think myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like this has ever happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira and the second kira have indeed made contact... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm in a dire pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira and the second kira have indeed made contact... I'm in a dire pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, right now, I'm probably incapable of calmly analyzing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could be doing this solely because I have no other suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, {\alpha&HFF&}if I am killed now, please conclude that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, if I am killed now, {\alpha&HFF&}please conclude that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, if I am killed now, please conclude that your son is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make another surprise attack, but it can't be helped... {\alpha&HFF&}this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make another surprise attack, but it can't be helped... this is now a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, I'm just pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-kun... hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yagami-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yagami-kun... hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I'd like to speak to him alone for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure this is okay? What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. You said you were "scared of showing your face in public", are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I realized I'd be fine as long as you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside, you're the only one who knows I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I'm killed within the next few days... {\alpha&HFF&}you are Kira. I've informed everyone at Headquarters of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I'm killed within the next few days... you are Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}I've informed everyone at Headquarters of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I'm killed within the next few days... you are Kira. I've informed everyone at Headquarters of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said yourself that it's lonely without me around, {\alpha&HFF&}so I thought I'd come in for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said yourself that it's lonely without me around, so I thought I'd come in for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I don't die, university is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when you're not around, there's no one I can talk to at my level. {\alpha&HFF&}It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when you're not around, there's no one I can talk to at my level. It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus the talented Takada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really be safe to kill him today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, by non-chalantly turning up like this, he's just trying to break my will to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably trying to warn me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just what he wants to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we grab some cake from the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got no lectures next period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they have shortcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a shoot nearby, so I thought I'd drop by!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, one of your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's wonderfully unique, isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wait... I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa can see Ryuuga's real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Light's girlfriend, Amane Misa. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuuga Hideki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's got the same name as the idol. Funny, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that's different from the name I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}this time, your decision to come out has worked against y--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, this time, your decision to come out has worked against y--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, he's realized?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he thinks there's a possibility that she's the second Kira, surely he wouldn't be able to laugh like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I'm very jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a fan of Misa's since the August edition of "Eighteen".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Really?! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, it's Misa-Misa, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It is Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Misa-Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always seem to get noticed when there's lots of young people around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I buy your stuff every month!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Someone just touched my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nerve! To take advantage of all this confusion to do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga-san, you're so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna feel too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out L's real name from Misa as soon as possible, but with all these people around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! {\alpha&HFF&}It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be late, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Misa leaves, all I need to do is make one phone call to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye Light! See you after work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we go, Yagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead, I need to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been all sorts of fun, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I was able to find out your real name and kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been all sorts of fun, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I was able to find out your real name and kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Hello"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like someone dropped this phone amid all the confusion just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time... he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Misa's phone. I'll return it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, {\alpha&HFF&}you may think you've outwitted me, but Misa has another cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, you may think you've outwitted me, {\alpha&HFF&}but Misa has another cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga, you may think you've outwitted me, but Misa has another cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I ring that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that right. We've done it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably both good and bad news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've apprehended Amane Misa on suspicion of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has he suspected Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she was caught so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the second Kira sent the video tapes from Amane's room, {\alpha&HFF&}they left a great deal of evidence, such as hairs and clothing fibres, stuck to packing tape used to seal the envelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the second Kira sent the video tapes from Amane's room, they left a great deal of evidence, such as hairs and clothing fibres, stuck to packing tape used to seal the envelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that announcing she's under suspicion of being the second Kira would cause public chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're saying she's gone to be questioned about the charges held against her manager for drug possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I doubt the public will find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those videos... {\alpha&HFF&}I should have ensure I destroyed the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those videos... I should have ensure I destroyed the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, by being around me, rather than hiding, Ryuuga managed to protect himself, and get right to the heart of the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gamble... I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight has just begun, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, has she said anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a visual of her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki... what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki... what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been apprehended on suspicion of being the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to take these precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that there was enough evidence in Amane's room to assure us that she's the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need a confession of how she kill people, {\alpha&HFF&}if she knows Kira, and if she knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need a confession of how she kill people, if she knows Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and if she knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we need a confession of how she kill people, if she knows Kira, and if she knows who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as you're careful, I won't mind if you use slightly dubious methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, as long as you're careful, I won't mind if you use slightly dubious methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her to spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Yagami-san, {\alpha&HFF&}please prepare yourself for the fact that I'll be bringing Light-kun in for questioning regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Yagami-san, please prepare yourself for the fact that I'll be bringing Light-kun in for questioning regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Amane has said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! Amane has said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and bring up a visual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! After three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! {\alpha&HFF&}Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might have been too much for a girl who's only around twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be her limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... {\alpha&HFF&}hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that you admit you are the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}I don't know anything about the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't know anything about the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore... {\alpha&HFF&}I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore... I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you could kill me in an instant if you wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you want me to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't endure this anymore, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill you, I'll kill Yagami Light too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all his faul--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... you're really willing to die for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! {\alpha&HFF&}If you won't kill me I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! If you won't kill me I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari! Don't let her bite her tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, she's not being manipulated by Kira just before she dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rem, {\alpha&HFF&}what do you want all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rem, what do you want all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}even though I offered to help Misa escape, she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, even though I offered to help Misa escape, she refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because she realized that she would be seen as having special powers, which would cause you trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she realized she was reaching the limits of her mentality, {\alpha&HFF&}she began to ask for me to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she realized she was reaching the limits of her mentality, she began to ask for me to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this, {\alpha&HFF&}because she wants to be loved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this, because she wants to be loved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she begged me to, there's no way I could kill Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to watch her suffer like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forfeiting ownership of the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you forfeit ownership of a Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}all the memories you have of it disappears completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you forfeit ownership of a Death Note, all the memories you have of it disappears completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would forget about all the people she's killed, {\alpha&HFF&}and the fact that Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would forget about all the people she's killed, and the fact that Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there would be no danger of her giving away your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, she would no longer be able to see Ryuk or myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.35,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,389)}A few hours earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}this means that you'll forget everything you know about Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, this means that you'll forget everything you know about Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human you love is Yagami Light. {\alpha&HFF&}Those feelings alone will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human you love is Yagami Light. Those feelings alone will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why you should give up ownership of your Death Note and entrust everything to Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is no longer the owner of a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that that was our sole option.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa has no memory of the Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}it's possible that she can be released.
